Package imagingbook.sampleimages

Enum Class GeneralSampleImage

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<GeneralSampleImage>
imagingbook.sampleimages.GeneralSampleImage
All Implemented Interfaces:
ImageResource, NamedResource, Serializable, Comparable<GeneralSampleImage>, Constable
public enum GeneralSampleImage extends Enum<GeneralSampleImage> implements ImageResource

Enumeration defining a set of ImageResource objects for selected sample images. Usage example: 

 import ij.process.ImageProcessor;
 import imagingbook.core.resource.ImageResource;
 import imagingbook.sampleimages.GeneralSampleImage;
 
 ImageResource ir = GeneralTestImage.Clown;
 ImageProcessor ip = ir.getImage().getProcessor();
 // process ip ...
